<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>: <span class="c2">(} الوَصْنَةُ)</span> :<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(أَهْمَلَهُ الجَوْهرِيُّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وقالَ ابنُ الأَعْرابيِّ:</span> هِيَ (الخِرْقَةُ الصَّغيرةُ) ،<span class="c5"> قالَ:</span> والصِّنْوةُ الفَسِيلَةُ،<span class="c5"> {والصّوْنَةُ:</span> العَتِيدَةُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
